=== Noun ===
'''atom''', plural '''[[atoms]]'''

# The smallest possible amount of matter which still retains its identity as a chemical element.  An atom consists of a [[nucleus]] containing [[proton]]s and (for all [[isotope]]s except Hydrogen-1) [[neutron]]s, surrounded by a cloud of [[electron]]s.

